'''Myōken-gū''' (妙見宮), '''Myōkendō''' (妙見堂), or '''Myōken Shrine''' (妙見神社) are [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in various regions of Japan. The enshrined deities are [[Ame-no-Minakanushi]] and the [[:en:North Star|North Star]].
* {{ill|Myōken Shrine (Tokyo)|ja|妙見神社 (東京都)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōken Shrine (Tokyo)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located on [[Myōken Island]]. * {{ill|Chiba Shrine|ja|千葉妙見宮|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 千葉神社}} - Located in [[:en:Chūō-ku, Chiba|Chūō-ku, Chiba]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Hoshida Myokengu|ja|星田妙見宮|3=小松神社_(交野市)|1=Hoshida Myokengu|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hoshida Myokengu|13=User:Immanuelle/Hoshida Myokengu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 小松神社 (交野市)}} - Located in [[:en:Katano|Katano]], [[:en:Osaka Prefecture|Osaka Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Iwaya Myōken-gū|ja|岩屋妙見宮|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwaya Myōken-gū|qq=}} - Located in [[Nio-chō]], [[:en:Mitoyo|Mitoyo]], [[:en:Kagawa Prefecture|Kagawa Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Myōken Shrine (Naruto)|ja|妙見神社 (鳴門市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōken Shrine (Naruto)|qq=}} - Located in [[Muyachō Hayashizaki]], [[:en:Naruto|Naruto]], [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Myōken-gū (Tōyō)|ja|妙見宮 (東洋町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōken-gū (Tōyō)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Shirahama, [[:en:Tōyō|Tōyō]], [[:en:Aki District|Aki District]], [[:en:Kōchi Prefecture|Kōchi Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Myōken-gū (Yatsushiro)|ja|妙見宮 (八代市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Myōken-gū (Yatsushiro)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 八代神社}} - Located in [[:en:Yatsushiro|Yatsushiro]], [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Mioya Shrine (Adachiyama Myōken-gū)|ja|御祖神社|1=Adachi Myokengu|2=ja|3=御祖神社|4=fr|5=Adachi Myokengu|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Adachiyama Myokengu|1=Adachi Myokengu|4=fr|5=Adachi Myokengu|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Adachiyama Myokengu|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mioya Shrine (Adachiyama Myōken-gū)|13=User:Immanuelle/Adachi Myokengu|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Kokurakita-ku|Kokurakita-ku]], [[:en:Kitakyushu|Kitakyushu]], [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]]. Since [[:en:1945|1945]], also known as the General Myōken Shrine of Japan. * Former name of {{ill|Taga Shrine (Nogata)|ja|多賀神社 (直方市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taga Shrine (Nogata)|qq=}} in [[:en:Nogata|Nogata]]. * {{ill|Katsuragi Shrine Myōken-gū|ja|葛城神社妙見宮|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Katsuragi Shrine Myōken-gū|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Chikujō|Chikujō]], [[Chikujō District]], [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]].
